Vilebrequin to Be Sold by Fashion Fund One, Sunday Times Reports

-- B y   A d a m   H a i g h
-- 
2011-07-24T06:06:17Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-07-24/vilebrequin-to-be-sold-by-fashion-fund-one-sunday-times-reports.html
Vilebrequin, the swimming trunks
brand, has been put up for sale by its private equity owners
Fashion Fund One, the Sunday Times newspaper reported, without
saying where it got the information.  Morgan Stanley is the leading candidate among investment
banks to manage the sale, the newspaper said.  To contact the reporter on this story:
Adam Haigh in London at 
 ahaigh1@bloomberg.net   To contact the editor responsible for this story:
Andrew Rummer at 
